===佛教===
列城人口比例最高的宗教为佛教，市域内有许多佛教建筑。

*[[提克西寺|提克西寺]]是一座[[藏传佛教|藏传佛教]][[格鲁派|格鲁派]]的寺院，位于[[列城|列城]]以东19公里的提克西村山顶<ref>Singh (2006), p.91</ref>。该寺与[[西藏|西藏]][[拉萨|拉萨]]的[[布达拉宫|布达拉宫]]相似而著称，是拉达克中部最大的寺庙。<ref name=Willis>{{cite web|last1=Willis|first1=Jan|title=The Cho-mos of Ladakh: From Servants to Practitioners|url=http://archive.thebuddhadharma.com/issues/2004/summer/willis.htm|publisher=Buddhadharma: The Practitioner's Quarterly|accessdate=2014-09-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140929170643/http://archive.thebuddhadharma.com/issues/2004/summer/willis.htm|archivedate=2014-09-29}}</ref><ref>Singh （2006），p.91 </ref>

*[[香提佛塔|香提佛塔]]由日本僧人兴建于1983年-1991年，以促进世界和平与繁荣，以及纪念佛教成立2500年，[[第十四世达赖喇嘛|第十四世达赖喇嘛]]于1991年8月为香提佛塔揭幕。<ref name="Temples">{{cite web|url=http://www.buddhist-temples.com/buddhist-monastery/ladakh/shanti-stupa.html|title=Shanti Stupa|publisher=Buddhist-temples.com|accessdate=2009-10-19|archive-date=2009-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091107155708/http://www.buddhist-temples.com/buddhist-monastery/ladakh/shanti-stupa.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name = "bhasin">{{cite book|last= Bhasin|first=Sanjeev Kumar|title=Amazing land Ladakh: places, people, and culture|pages=119–20|chapter=Shanti Stupa|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8IZloNzI8BgC&pg=PA120&dq=shanti+stupa+Ladakh&as_brr=3&client=firefox-a#v=onepage&q=shanti%20stupa%20Ladakh&f=false | isbn=978-81-7387-186-3 | year=2006 | publisher=Indus Publishing}}</ref><ref name="bajwa">{{cite book|last= Jagir Singh Bajwa, Ravinder Kaur|title=Tourism Management|pages=117|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TVXCiwdwPxsC&pg=PA117&dq=shanti+stupa+Ladakh&lr=&as_brr=3&client=firefox-a#v=onepage&q=shanti%20stupa%20Ladakh&f=false | isbn=978-81-313-0047-3 | year=2007 | publisher=APH Publishing}}</ref>《[[印度教徒报|印度教徒报]]》称它是列城周围“最著名的旅游胜地”。

